data.description: Welcome to your stunning lakefront oasis in the highly sought-after Botanica Lakes community! This luxurious 4 bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers resort-style living in a family-friendly, gated neighborhood.Walk through this beautiful home and be greeted by breathtaking views of the tranquil lake, providing a sense of calm & serenity.   The spacious living areas are perfect for entertaining guests or simply relaxing with your loved ones.  The kitchen,features modern appliances,(LG smart stainless) ample counter space,& convenient breakfast bar. Imagine preparing delicious meals while gazing out at the shimmering waters of the lake.  Step outside and take in the breathtaking scenery. Sipping your morning coffee or hosting a barbecue, The  backyard leads down to the water's edge, where you can unwind while taking in the sights and sounds of nature.    The Botanica Lakes community offers an array of amenities, including a sparkling community pool, a fitness center, & tennis courts, fostering a true sense of community and belonging.Conveniently located near shopping, dining, and entertainment. This home provides the perfect combination of luxury, comfort, and convenience.
